                  Johnston.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1862 January 4</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:3</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>Lt. Col. Philip P. Slaughter to Stuart (recovering
